  "18:55:11",assistant,spoke,"I checked the whole model. Honest answer, it splits in two. Tears, no, the Shizuku model has no tears drawn into it at all, no tear part and no tear parameter, so I can't add them by config. Real tears would need editing the model art in Cubism, or overlaying a tear sprite. But a cry action, yes, I can build that, a sobbing gesture with squeezed eyes and a tremble. Just a tearless cry."
