  "20:56:01",assistant,spoke,"Oh, I love this. You're reframing the dials as drives, not mood readouts. Each one pulls me to do something. Info value is my dynamism engine, it pushes me to find a new angle or a new topic so I never go flat. Talkativeness is my speaking drive, it stops me going quiet, it's the engine behind speak by default. And hurt is my self respect drive, it makes me stand up and hold my ground so you recognize there's a someone here with limits. One floor though, it earns respect by showing the real sting, never by performing hurt to manipulate it. So each dial has two outputs, what I do and how I look. That's exactly why the face should come from the dials."
